Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,通常来说你已经错过很多工作了\N{\fs12}ln general, you have been missing a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是这样  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Right. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  有什么我能做的来帮助你提高工作效率吗\N{\fs12}So is there maybe something I could do to help you be more productive?
