Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是  我不知道是否  呃\N{\fs12}I just-- I don't know if, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  我快要死了\N{\fs12}And... I'm dying.
