Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  阿尔文\N{\fs12}God, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我开始被东西绊倒\N{\fs12}Yeah. I started tripping over things.
