Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了  儿子\N{\fs12}What the hell, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  我去不了了\N{\fs12}I'm sorry. I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道我们在这件事上花了四万三千美元\N{\fs12}Do you realize we're spending $43,000 on this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,实在抱歉  但是我得和阿尔文去洛杉矶\N{\fs12}I'm sorry, but I have to go to L.A. with Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么啊  - 是私事\N{\fs12}- Why? - It's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 我不能说\N{\fs12}- What? - I can't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟社区服务有什么关系吗\N{\fs12}What, does this have to do with that community service?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不  只是私事\N{\fs12}No. It's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子  你看  这整个想法的目的是\N{\fs12}Son, look, the whole idea here is to--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,建立一点公司的士气\N{\fs12}is to build a little company morale...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让你在公司的核心位置\N{\fs12}with you right in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗  我必须得走\N{\fs12}All right? I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等回来我再跟你解释\N{\fs12}And I'll explain when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等一下\N{\fs12}Wait a minute. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在能离开我们州吗\N{\fs12}Are you even allowed to leave the State?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我一会就到  别担心\N{\fs12}No, I'll be there. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给我打电话啊  我会去的\N{\fs12}Just call me. I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那一会再跟你聊  好吗\N{\fs12}Okay, I'll talk to you later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  拜\N{\fs12}Okay. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么进这间办公室的\N{\fs12}How did you get in this office?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个预约\N{\fs12}I have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这个门是开着的\N{\fs12}The door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是开着的\N{\fs12}No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我到的时候就是开着的\N{\fs12}It was when I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候到的\N{\fs12}When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上  阿尔文在哪\N{\fs12}This morning. Where's Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么名字  - 蒂凡尼\N{\fs12}- What's your name? - Tiffany.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蒂凡尼什么  - 阿尔文在哪\N{\fs12}- Tiffany what? - Where's Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文不在这工作了\N{\fs12}Alvin doesn't work here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文走了吗  - 是的  他退休了\N{\fs12}- Alvin's gone? - Yeah, he's retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  等一下\N{\fs12}Hey, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你要去哪儿\N{\fs12}Wait a second. Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在飞往洛杉矶的三号航班\N{\fs12}Now boarding flight Three to Los Angeles,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,头等舱和星级里程会员请登机\N{\fs12}first Class and Star Mileage members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也欢迎商务舱的乘客登机\N{\fs12}We'd also like to welcome our Business Class passengers at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你看  阿尔文  我们可能得登机了\N{\fs12}Ah, you know, Alvin, we should probably board now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道卢·格里克开过一百多次\N{\fs12}Did you know that Lou·Gehrig drove in more than a hundred runs--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  你告诉过我\N{\fs12}Yeah, you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,连续2130场比赛  一整天\N{\fs12}Played in 2, 130 consecutive games, and one day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是让自己脱离了阵容\N{\fs12}he just takes himself out of the line-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  - 2130场比赛\N{\fs12}- Alvin... - 2, 130 consecutive games--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-阿尔文  - 来了\N{\fs12}- Alvin. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  想像一下\N{\fs12}I mean, imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拿票了吗  - 拿了\N{\fs12}- You have your ticket? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不好意思  - 这真的太棒了\N{\fs12}- Excuse me. - This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没飞过头等舱\N{\fs12}I've never flown First Class before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 麻烦让一下  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Excuse me. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉  - 劳驾\N{\fs12}- I'm sorry. - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早上好\N{\fs12}Good morning, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,早\N{\fs12}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有一个信封\N{\fs12}You all have envelopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有一个卡片  上面写着一个词或词组\N{\fs12}lnside is a card with a word or a phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  打开你们的信封\N{\fs12}Go ahead. Open your envelopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  请各位在屋子的四周走动\N{\fs12}Now, I want you to walk around the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,将自己重新介绍给你们的同事  再问问他们  他们的词是什么\N{\fs12}Reintroduce yourself to your co-workers and ask them what their word is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后找就会找到你的搭档\N{\fs12}You'll know when you've found a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fs12}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 花生酱  - 通心粉\N{\fs12}- Peanut butter. - Macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的是什么  - 葡萄\N{\fs12}- What do you have? - Grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,通心粉\N{\fs12}Macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 花生酱  - 不是\N{\fs12}- Peanut butter. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是通心粉吗  - 果冻\N{\fs12}- Macaroni?\N{\fs12}- Jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当你找到你的搭档  也就找到了你的周末室友\N{\fs12}When you've found your match, you've found your weekend roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 花生酱  - 最近怎么样\N{\fs12}- Peanut butter. - How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  花生酱\N{\fs12}Uh, peanut butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好吧  果冻\N{\fs12}Oh, well, jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  好吧\N{\fs12}Great. Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们往这边飞的时候你向下看了吗\N{\fs12}Did you look down when we were flying in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的一个地方真的是太赞了\N{\fs12}Amazing, the possibilities of a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,闻到茉莉香了吗\N{\fs12}Smell that-- jasmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\N{\fs12}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有美女们  哦  我的天啊\N{\fs12}And the women... Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信\N{\fs12}They're unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打开广播吧\N{\fs12}Let's turn on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦  摇滚  太大声了吗  抱歉\N{\fs12}Wow, rock 'n' roll. Too loud? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Thank you. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那  去酒店吧  我们早点办理入住\N{\fs12}So... go to the hotel, got us an early check-in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看看游泳池  吃点午餐  然后  谁知道呢\N{\fs12}check out the pool, little lunch, and then... who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,棒极了\N{\fs12}Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不介意跟我同住\N{\fs12}Hope you don't mind sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫这个总统套房\N{\fs12}They call this the Presidential Suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知  查克·D和弗拉瓦·弗拉夫在这时就住在这\N{\fs12}I understand that Chuck·D and Flava·Flav stay here when they're in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说弗拉瓦·弗拉夫\N{\fs12}Did you say Flava Flav?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你知道的  《国民公敌》里面的嘛\N{\fs12}Yeah, you know... Public Enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是给你的\N{\fs12}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 非常感谢  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Thank you very much. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦  阿尔文  这间房间太贵了\N{\fs12}Wow, Alvin, this is a very expensive room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我请客  - 这是你的单身派对\N{\fs12}- My treat. - It's your bachelor party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我应该我买单的  - 不  不用  我来付\N{\fs12}- I should be paying for this. - No. No-no, I'm paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你认真的吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Are you sure? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  呃  我就是想谢谢你\N{\fs12}Hey, uh... I just want to thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,能陪我来这\N{\fs12}for coming here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  会很有意思的\N{\fs12}Ah, it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  -嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上蒂凡尼·斯科维奇来你的给办公室了\N{\fs12}Tiffany·Skovich was in your office this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我觉得是她闯进来的\N{\fs12}Right. I think she broke in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太奇怪了\N{\fs12}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  我觉得她是睡在这里了\N{\fs12}Actually, I think she slept here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果她再来这  给我打电话或者直接打给警察\N{\fs12}Well, if she comes by again, call me or call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  你知道  我看过她的档案\N{\fs12}Okay. You know, I read her file.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真是令人惊讶  她是个妓女\N{\fs12}It's kind of surprising that she's a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她还这么年轻\N{\fs12}She's so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她还能回到简之家吗\N{\fs12}ls she going to be able to go back to Jane's Place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  昨天她被开除了\N{\fs12}No. She was expelled yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们转移她之前逃跑了\N{\fs12}Ran off before we could transfer her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  所以她是要去哪里呢\N{\fs12}Hm... so where is she going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,少管所  一旦我们找到她  真是太遗憾了\N{\fs12}Juvie... once we find her. It's a shame, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对于她这样的女孩来说  简之家是一个再好不过的地方了\N{\fs12}Jane's Place is as good as it gets for a girl with her record.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她错过了一个好机会\N{\fs12}She blew a great chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  太冷了\N{\fs12}Oh, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,冻死了  冻死了  冻死了  冻死了 冻死了\N{\fs12}Cold-- cold-- cold-- cold. Cold-- cold-- cold-- cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈  暖和\N{\fs12}Aah... hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太暖和了\N{\fs12}Hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不来游泳吗  - 不  我有些工作还需要弄\N{\fs12}- You're not going to swim? - No. I've got some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哈\N{\fs12}Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哈\N{\fs12}Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我真真实实的感受到周围的水\N{\fs12}I can really feel the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我在说什么吗\N{\fs12}You know what I'm talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为某些原因  我在这感觉更好一点\N{\fs12}l-- I feel better here, for some reason. Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我应该搬来洛杉矶住\N{\fs12}Maybe I should just move to Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许吧  - 不\N{\fs12}- Maybe. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会想死你们这群家伙的  - 我们也会想你\N{\fs12}- I'd miss you guys too much. - Miss you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你太放不开了\N{\fs12}You don't open up much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候我会想知道  是不是我或者\N{\fs12}I just wonder sometimes, is it me or is--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是我自己的原因\N{\fs12}No, it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  咱们走吧\N{\fs12}Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 兄弟  我们今天有很多事情要做\N{\fs12}- What? - We got a lot to do, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很多事情  快点\N{\fs12}A lot to do. Come on.
