Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,团队运动  阿尔文  并不是  你是到  并不适合我\N{\fs12}Team sports, Alvin, not really, you know, my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,威尼斯海滩\N{\fs12}Venice Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方很有传奇色彩\N{\fs12}This place is legendary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的球员都在这玩\N{\fs12}All the ballers played here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样都是很严肃的事\N{\fs12}The serious ones anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,马库斯·约翰逊  拜伦·斯科特  克里斯·米尔斯\N{\fs12}Marcus·Johnson, Byron·Scott, Chris·Mills,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 菲利普  辣酱  冠军  - 你知道的  阿尔文  是很有意思\N{\fs12}- Philip ''Hot Sauce'' Champion. - You know, Alvin, that was fun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我需要回酒店  然后有几个电话要打\N{\fs12}but I've got to get back to the hotel and make some calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  咱们去游泳吧\N{\fs12}No. Let's go swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,穿什么\N{\fs12}ln what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快来吧  尼克  你在害怕什么\N{\fs12}Come on, Nick. What're you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你穿着你的内裤呢  - 然后呢\N{\fs12}- You're in your underwear. - So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那小不点也这样穿的\N{\fs12}So's that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  你来吗\N{\fs12}Come on. You comin' in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你去吧\N{\fs12}You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs12}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我的天哪\N{\fs12}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  呃  你想留浴室的灯吗\N{\fs12}Oh. Uh., do you want the bathroom light on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不用  怎么了  你需要吗\N{\fs12}No, I don't. Why? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  有时候当我在一个陌生的地方\N{\fs12}Oh, sometimes when I'm in a new place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好吧  当然  你想开着  那就开着吧\N{\fs12}Oh, yeah, sure. You want it on, leave it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 那太好了\N{\fs12}Okay. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伯顿  - 怎么了\N{\fs12}- Burton? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克怎么了\N{\fs12}What happened with Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  他得去\N{\fs12}Oh, he had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,去洛杉矶\N{\fs12}go to Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 洛杉矶吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Los Angeles? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有些私事\N{\fs12}Some personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他还好吗  - 是的  他很好\N{\fs12}- Is he okay? - Yeah. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好  我们很惦记他\N{\fs12}Well, good. A few of us were concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  今天过得真开心啊\N{\fs12}Hmm. What a fantastic day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说  那是\N{\fs12}I mean, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  那是一个明星坐在你后面呢吗\N{\fs12}Hey, is that someone famous sitting behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是个明星\N{\fs12}I think that's someone famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  有可能是吧\N{\fs12}Well, maybe it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 凯撒做的真不错  - 嗯\N{\fs12}- This is a very good Caesar. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你什么时候结婚呢\N{\fs12}So when're you getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还没定日子  我就是昨天问了她一下  所以\N{\fs12}Haven't set a date yet. I just asked her yesterday, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没有告诉她吗\N{\fs12}You didn't tell her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,其实  我去她的办公室想要告诉她  但是之后\N{\fs12}Well, I went to her office to tell her but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fs12}the clarity--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这个消息让我明白一点  我只想和她在一起\N{\fs12}The news gave, me this clarity and I just had to ask her to stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且使我坚定了这个想法\N{\fs12}And... it was powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要收拾走吗  - 哦  谢谢\N{\fs12}- May I? - Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  味道非常好\N{\fs12}Thank you. That was dee-licious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你相信治疗师吗  - 你想说什么样的\N{\fs12}- Do you believe in healers? - Like what? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  有的人有治疗的力量\N{\fs12}Well, people who have healing powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以  呃  通过意念或者能量做一些事情\N{\fs12}who can, uh, do things with energy or thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,据说有人就有这样的天赋\N{\fs12}Supposedly there are people who have gifts like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我读了一些令人难以置信的故事  我猜有的时候真的有效\N{\fs12}I've been reading incredible stories and sometimes it works, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  你不相信吗  - 我\N{\fs12}- What? You don't think it can? - l.. .
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我怎么想的吗  尼克\N{\fs12}You know what I think, Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得埃里克·埃斯特拉达就坐在那\N{\fs12}I think that's Erik·Estrada sitting over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  埃里克\N{\fs12}Hey, Erik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fs12}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂凡尼  在那等着\N{\fs12}Tiffany, wait right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fs12}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识了一个男孩\N{\fs12}I met a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫克林特\N{\fs12}His name's Clint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fs12}We--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要出去\N{\fs12}We're going out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,约会\N{\fs12}dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他上的是普通高中\N{\fs12}He goes to a regular high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢踢足球\N{\fs12}He plays soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸是一名医生\N{\fs12}His dad's a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有告诉他我住在哪\N{\fs12}I haven't told him where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  他把我放到沙迪赛德的一个房子门口\N{\fs12}So he... drops me outside a house in Shadyside and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,之后  我走回简之家\N{\fs12}then I walk back to Jane's Place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很多次都错过了宵禁  所以他们把我赶了出来\N{\fs12}I've missed so many curfews, they kicked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  嗯\N{\fs12}You know, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,最后  你总归得跟他实话实说\N{\fs12}...eventually, you would have to tell him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说我是一个妓女吗\N{\fs12}That I was a hooker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,并不会像你想象的一样好\N{\fs12}Doesn't exactly go over as well as you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  蒂凡尼  有这样一个\N{\fs12}Well, Tiffany-- there-- there's, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个你的扣押令  所以\N{\fs12}there's an attachment order out for you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我需要进少管所\N{\fs12}I know. I'm going to Juvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我  我需要联系你的社工\N{\fs12}Yeah. l-- I have to call your social worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事  今天晚上有一个舞会\N{\fs12}Thing is... there's this dance tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他邀请我参加春季舞会  我也特别想去\N{\fs12}He invited me to the Spring Dance, and I really want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我知道这可能听起来很愚蠢\N{\fs12}Look, l-- I know it may sound stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我从来没有参加过一次真正舞会\N{\fs12}but I've never been to a real dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  这是一个感同身受的练习\N{\fs12}Okay, this is an empathy exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克将宣读事先准备好的声明\N{\fs12}Jake will read from three prepared statements...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,给他的搭档  伯顿  在这种情况下\N{\fs12}to his partner-- Burton, in this case--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,然后伯顿需要应答\N{\fs12}and Burton will respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 可以吗\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像你在办公室  杰克有问题过来找你\N{\fs12}As though you were in your office and Jake was coming to you with a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  好的  -  明白了吗\N{\fs12}- Oh, okay. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 杰克\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再跟这个客户合作了\N{\fs12}''l can't work with that client anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的很没有礼貌\N{\fs12}''He's rude and disrespectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他好像把我当成了清洁工  而不是律师\N{\fs12}He treats me like I'm a cleaning woman, not an attorney.''
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,面对这种情况  你会要怎么说  伯顿\N{\fs12}What would you say to that, Burton?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  呃  客户是一个\N{\fs12}Well, uh, a client is a--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一个混蛋客户  但是  呃\N{\fs12}is a damn client, and, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  我们不能感情用事\N{\fs12}You know, we're not in the-- in the feeling business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在处理法律业务  所以  如果他不能处理好\N{\fs12}We're in the law business, so if he couldn't handle it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我请他找能处理好的人来做\N{\fs12}I would ask him to refer it to someone who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  伯顿\N{\fs12}Okay, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这类问题的另一个解决方法\N{\fs12}Another approach to this kind of problem
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可以是成为你同事的一面镜子\N{\fs12}would be to act as a mirror to your colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢\N{\fs12}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,比如  你可以说\N{\fs12}Well, for instance, you could say,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  听起来你是真的很不开心啊\N{\fs12}''Jake, you sound like you're really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,能跟我说说发生了什么吗\N{\fs12}Can you tell me what happened?''
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  这样杰克就会觉得你是站在他这边的  而且他的心情对你来说是很重要的\N{\fs12}You see, that way Jake knows that you're on his team and that his feelings matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Okay. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  读下一个\N{\fs12}Jake, read another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心自己有没有在这周完成工作的能力\N{\fs12}''I'm worried about my ability to finish my work this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈生病了  而且我的妻子也有些不舒服  待在家里\N{\fs12}My mother is sick, and my wife is having some problems at home.''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那   我可能会说   我  听到这个消息我很难受\N{\fs12}Well, I would certainly say, ''I'm-- I'm sorry to hear that.''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那么接下来我又得说  你知道的\N{\fs12}And I would say, you know, again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得你解决不了  那么\N{\fs12}''if you feel like you can't handle it, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,过来跟我说  我  我会找一个能做到的人来做\N{\fs12}come tell me, and I'll-- I'll find someone who can.''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  你有什么感受  告诉他\N{\fs12}Jake. How's that make you feel? Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道  他平时就是这样的\N{\fs12}I don't know. He's just being himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但是你试着说一下你自己的感受\N{\fs12}Right, but try to talk about your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当伯顿说  他会找别人来代替你完成工作\N{\fs12}when Burton tells you he's going to refer your work to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己可以完成\N{\fs12}''l would rather finish it myself.''
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想要一个成功的机会  - 当然\N{\fs12}- You want a chance to succeed. - 'Course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你更想要一些鼓励\N{\fs12}You would like some encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么笑\N{\fs12}Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我的意思是  这并不是  呃\N{\fs12}Well, no, I mean, that's just not, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我  我的意思是  法林&法林律师事务所并不是完全像这样工作\N{\fs12}l-- l-- I mean, Fallin & Fallin doesn't exactly work like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  这是什么意思呢\N{\fs12}Well, what does-- what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么  我只是想说  那就是  就是\N{\fs12}Nothing. I mean, that's just-- just the way-- it's the way--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  就现在\N{\fs12}Jake. Now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他\N{\fs12}Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,各位  这就是我们来到这的原因\N{\fs12}That's why we're here, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我想说  在这种情况下\N{\fs12}Okay. Well, I mean, in this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜  嗯\N{\fs12}I guess, that, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会换掉我  然后让尼克来接手这个案子\N{\fs12}you would probably take me off this deal and give it to Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不  等一下\N{\fs12}No. Wait. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  杰克在试着跟你说他的感受\N{\fs12}Burton, Jake is trying to tell you how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  但是  我  我认为\N{\fs12}I understand that, but, l-- I think, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说  凭良心讲\N{\fs12}I think I can honestly say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直尽量公平对待每一个人\N{\fs12}that I have always tried to treat everybody the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是每一个人\N{\fs12}Everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许试了  但是并没有做到\N{\fs12}You may try but you-- you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会这么说\N{\fs12}How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧  伯顿\N{\fs12}Come on, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说  我们在这  困在这个地方\N{\fs12}I mean, here we are, stuck in this place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,做一些将心比心的练习  而\N{\fs12}doing empathy exercises and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克在洛杉矶\N{\fs12}Nick is in L.A...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,玩\N{\fs12}having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 点心怎么样  - 还不错\N{\fs12}- How 'bout that dim sum? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啊  好东西  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Yeah, good stuff. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的这些  但是早餐有点奇怪\N{\fs12}All those trays. Weird breakfast food, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼  和糯米\N{\fs12}The fish, the sticky rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢\N{\fs12}I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有个人  廖先生\N{\fs12}There's this guy, Dr. Liao,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来自北京边上一个小镇子\N{\fs12}from a small town outside of Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,据说他有一些特异功能\N{\fs12}He's supposed to have special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,世界各地的人都去找他\N{\fs12}People come to see him from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我从网上肌萎缩侧索硬化交流群里一个女人那了解到他\N{\fs12}I heard about him from some woman I met online, with ALS.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她七年前得的这个病  但是现在还能正常生活\N{\fs12}She's had it for seven years. She still leads a pretty normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她去找到他  他解救了她\N{\fs12}She says she came to see him, and he helped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我来洛杉矶的原因之一  为了找到他\N{\fs12}That's one of the reasons I came to Los Angeles, to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你预约了吗  - 是的  二十分钟之后\N{\fs12}- Do you have an appointment? - Yeah. In twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那  我一会来找你  - 不  我  我想一起去\N{\fs12}- So uh, I can just meet you later. - No, l-- I want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fs12}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信  我刚吃完\N{\fs12}I can't believe it. I just ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在又饿了\N{\fs12}I'm already hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,马斯特森先生吗\N{\fs12}Mr. Masterson?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\fs12}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快  下来  让我  看一看\N{\fs12}Well, come down. Let me... take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.41,0:23:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮\N{\fs12}It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这样觉得吗  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Think so? - Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果  如果你想的话  我觉得我楼上可能有一些你会喜欢的东西\N{\fs12}lf-- If you want, I think I might have some things upstairs that you might like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  来吧\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜想我已经好了\N{\fs12}I guess I'm healed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  卢·格里克  到梅奥诊所给自己检查了一下\N{\fs12}So Lou Gehrig-- checks himself into the Mayo Clinic,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,得到诊断之后  又回到了洋基体育馆\N{\fs12}gets diagnosed, then goes back to Yankee Stadium,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在数千人面前做了演讲\N{\fs12}makes a speech in front of thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.72,0:24:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 说他自己是多么的幸运  - 我看过那场演讲\N{\fs12}- Says how lucky he is. - I've seen the speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,两年之后  格里克死了\N{\fs12}Two years later, Gehrig's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.30,0:24:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,37岁\N{\fs12}Thirty-seven years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.69,0:24:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  请带我们去回声公园\N{\fs12}Uh, can you please take us to Echo Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.73,0:24:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,滨海大道1023号\N{\fs12}1023 Esplanade Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.30,0:24:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  好的  先生  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Oh, yes sir. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.45,0:24:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去回声公园做什么\N{\fs12}What's at Echo Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.92,0:24:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  我有没有跟你说过我的儿子\N{\fs12}Did l, uh... ever tell you about my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.17,0:24:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有娶他的妈妈\N{\fs12}I never married his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.42,0:24:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们处过一段  之后  呃\N{\fs12}We had a brief fling and then, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.63,0:24:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她怀孕了\N{\fs12}she got pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.74,0:24:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是15年前的事了\N{\fs12}That was almost 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.11,0:25:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是么\N{\fs12}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.46,0:25:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我上次见他时  他才7岁  现在应该上高中了\N{\fs12}Last time I saw him, he was seven. He must be in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.83,0:25:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我不知道该不该这么做\N{\fs12}Oh... I don't know if I should do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.14,0:25:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不  阿尔文  你应该这样做\N{\fs12}No, Alvin, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我就\N{\fs12}I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.56,0:25:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该这样做的\N{\fs12}You should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说什么呢  说我刚好在这边吗\N{\fs12}Just tell him what? l-- I was in the neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.40,0:25:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就  就直接告诉他  你想见他\N{\fs12}Just-- just tell him that you want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.53,0:25:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是么  - 我的意思是  你不需要说为什么的\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - I mean, you don't have to say why.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.39,0:25:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.01,0:25:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,詹妮弗\N{\fs12}Jennifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.79,0:26:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这么快\N{\fs12}That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.36,0:26:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想见我\N{\fs12}Didn't want to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.37,0:26:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他都不肯从房间出来\N{\fs12}Wouldn't come out of his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.77,0:26:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说他已经有爸爸了\N{\fs12}Said he already has a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.82,0:26:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回酒店吧\N{\fs12}Let's go back to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.03,0:26:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点累了\N{\fs12}I'm kind of tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.11,0:27:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂凡尼  他到了\N{\fs12}Tiffany. He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.24,0:27:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  你真漂亮\N{\fs12}Wow. You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.19,0:27:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你真的很漂亮  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- You look really great. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.86,0:27:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那  呃  好好玩\N{\fs12}Okay, well, uh, have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.90,0:27:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是12点之前要回家\N{\fs12}But you be home by midnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.59,0:27:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,否则的话  你知道的  我就得报警了\N{\fs12}or you know I'm going to have to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.61,0:27:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.94,0:27:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 好啦\N{\fs12}- Thank you. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.77,0:27:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜  - 拜\N{\fs12}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.04,0:27:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  我回来了  - 我在这\N{\fs12}- Alvin. I'm back. - I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.64,0:27:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你没跟我说游泳池是热的\N{\fs12}You didn't tell me the pool was heated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.43,0:27:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉我在走廊看到了吉娜·戴维斯\N{\fs12}You know, I think I saw Geena·Davis in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.78,0:28:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么  在收拾行李吗\N{\fs12}What're you doing? You packing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.51,0:28:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 十点有一趟航班  - 什么  单身聚会结束了吗\N{\fs12}- There's a 10:00flight. - What, the party's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.10,0:28:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.97,0:28:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  那这个我该怎么处理呢\N{\fs12}Ah, what am I going to do with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.99,0:28:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,湖人的票\N{\fs12}Laker tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.33,0:28:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,场边  今晚的\N{\fs12}Courtside. Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.83,0:28:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一张票1900美金\N{\fs12}You paid $1,900 a ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.52,0:28:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 花了这些钱吗  - 哦  尼克\N{\fs12}- Is that what they cost? - Oh, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.73,0:28:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,退了吧\N{\fs12}Return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.85,0:28:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  来吧  是湖人的  场边哦\N{\fs12}Alvin, come on. It's the Lakers-- courtside.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.51,0:28:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,跟杰克聊会天  然后去吃些寿司\N{\fs12}Have a chat with Jack. Go and get some Sushi afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.35,0:28:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不了  谢谢  - 你确定\N{\fs12}- Thanks, no. - Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.00,0:28:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想回家\N{\fs12}I just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.18,0:28:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  好的 算了吧  去他的湖人\N{\fs12}All right. Okay. Fine. Screw the Lakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.33,0:28:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我们  我们出去走走\N{\fs12}We'll, uh-- we'll go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.80,0:28:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以就聊聊  在逛一逛  然后吃点东西\N{\fs12}We can just talk about this and hang out, get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.07,0:28:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.38,0:28:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你不能把我拽来这里  在把我丢在这不管\N{\fs12}Alvin, you can't drag me across the country and then just drop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.98,0:28:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道匹兹堡现在有多冷么\N{\fs12}You know how cold it is in Pittsburgh now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.15,0:28:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是31度  31度\N{\fs12}It's 31 degrees, right now, 31 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.76,0:28:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  好吧\N{\fs12}Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.20,0:28:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去吃晚饭  你来选地方\N{\fs12}We'll get some dinner. You pick the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.12,0:28:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 我正要出去走走\N{\fs12}- Good. - I'm just going to go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.35,0:28:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己吗\N{\fs12}On your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.33,0:28:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  如果你不介意的话\N{\fs12}Yeah, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.42,0:28:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不介意\N{\fs12}I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.62,0:29:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  关于今天\N{\fs12}Burton, about today...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.92,0:29:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.96,0:29:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  我就是\N{\fs12}I'm sorry, I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.71,0:29:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我道歉\N{\fs12}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.82,0:29:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我说的话没有太过分\N{\fs12}And I hope what I said wasn't out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.41,0:29:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个家伙想让我们说  所以\N{\fs12}Well, that guy wanted us to talk, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.38,0:29:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  说起来\N{\fs12}You know, that said...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.66,0:29:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不觉得这个竞技场是公平的\N{\fs12}I don't feel that the playing field is level.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.01,0:29:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我为客户着想\N{\fs12}I mean, I land clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.05,0:29:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了比别人更多的时间\N{\fs12}I bill more hours than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.96,0:29:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,无论什么时候  我都尽量帮忙\N{\fs12}l-- I help out whenever needed,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.09,0:29:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让我做什么  我就做什么\N{\fs12}and I do whatever I'm asked to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.21,0:29:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  但是  尼克依然是\N{\fs12}and-- and still Nick is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.56,0:30:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的上级\N{\fs12}senior to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.94,0:30:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你在考虑更换管理层\N{\fs12}You're considering a management change.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.88,0:30:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我知道的\N{\fs12}l-- I know that and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.95,0:30:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道  尼克肯定是\N{\fs12}I know that Nick is clearly the--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.64,0:30:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,继承人\N{\fs12}the heir apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还不一定  杰克\N{\fs12}Not necessarily, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.78,0:30:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果  如果真的是这样\N{\fs12}Well, if-- if-- if that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.68,0:30:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该考虑考虑我\N{\fs12}you should consider me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.08,0:30:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你回来了\N{\fs12}Hey. You're back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.16,0:30:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fs12}How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.57,0:30:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把健身房弄的像夏威夷一样\N{\fs12}They made the gym look like it was Hawaiian.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.70,0:30:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有沙子和火把\N{\fs12}Sand and torches.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.66,0:30:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  不是真的火把\N{\fs12}I mean, they weren't real torches.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.76,0:30:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还有音乐\N{\fs12}And the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.97,0:30:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错\N{\fs12}That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.91,0:30:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,普通高中的女孩看起来很不同\N{\fs12}Girls at regular high school are so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.24,0:30:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了吗\N{\fs12}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.75,0:31:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候生宝宝啊\N{\fs12}When's your baby coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.00,0:31:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有几个月\N{\fs12}ln a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.87,0:31:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩还是女孩呢\N{\fs12}Boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.60,0:31:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我怎么了  蒂凡尼\N{\fs12}Tell me what's going on, Tiffany.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.93,0:31:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我全跟克林特说了  - 哦\N{\fs12}- I told Clint the truth. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.52,0:31:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,说了我怎么会沦落到简之家\N{\fs12}About how I ended up in Jane's Place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.91,0:31:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有少管所的事儿\N{\fs12}About Juvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.66,0:31:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的事情\N{\fs12}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.41,0:31:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.39,0:31:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一会之后  他什么都没跟我说\N{\fs12}He kind of stopped talking to me after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.29,0:31:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只和他的朋友们喝酒\N{\fs12}Drank with his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.72,0:31:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我鸡\N{\fs12}Called me a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.47,0:31:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就走了\N{\fs12}So I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.07,0:31:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,走回家\N{\fs12}Walked home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.91,0:31:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.97,0:31:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  是个男孩还是女孩呢\N{\fs12}So... are you having a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.93,0:32:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文\N{\fs12}Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.63,0:32:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我都想你了\N{\fs12}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,肌萎缩性脊髓侧索硬化症\N{\fs12}Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.47,0:32:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是个希腊词组\N{\fs12}It's a Greek phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.35,0:32:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A的意思是负的\N{\fs12}''A'' meaning negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.66,0:32:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Myo的意思是肌肉\N{\fs12}''Myo'' meaning muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.97,0:32:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trophic的意思是营养\N{\fs12}''Trophic'' meaning nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我正试着不去想它\N{\fs12}I'm trying to get my mind around it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.90,0:32:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,运动神经元退化\N{\fs12}Motor neurons degenerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,直到大脑不能给肌肉传递冲动\N{\fs12}until the brain can't send impulses to the muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.97,0:33:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,当肌肉无法接受这些信息  就会萎缩\N{\fs12}When the muscles can't receive messages, they atrophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.23,0:33:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我的大脑\N{\fs12}And my brain--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.56,0:33:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大脑还是那样\N{\fs12}my brain stays the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.42,0:33:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.61,0:33:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  尼克\N{\fs12}So Nick...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.56,0:33:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在想\N{\fs12}I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.14,0:33:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以向西游到多远\N{\fs12}of seeing how far west I could swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.63,0:33:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我能不能做到\N{\fs12}I don't know if I have it in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.31,0:33:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那维多利亚怎么办\N{\fs12}What about Victoria?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.09,0:33:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  她会她会离开的\N{\fs12}Oh... she's going to walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.58,0:33:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,至少她应该\N{\fs12}At least she should.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.58,0:33:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我在想什么\N{\fs12}I mean, what was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.69,0:33:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是\N{\fs12}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.54,0:33:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要死了\N{\fs12}I am going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.99,0:33:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要死了  尼克\N{\fs12}I am going to die, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.23,0:33:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\fs12}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.65,0:34:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用坐在这的\N{\fs12}You don't have to sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我明白的\N{\fs12}I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.78,0:34:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我都好了\N{\fs12}Alvin, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.87,0:34:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我正要下楼到打听等着\N{\fs12}Uh... I'm just going to head down to the lobby and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.00,0:34:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要定一辆出租车吗  - 已经有一辆豪华轿车了\N{\fs12}- Shall I call a cab? - Already got us a limo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.73,0:34:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 楼下见  - 好的\N{\fs12}- I'll see you down there. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.91,0:35:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs12}One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.75,0:35:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了  尼克\N{\fs12}I'm coming, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.53,0:35:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抵达航班的旅客\N{\fs12}Arriving passengers on flight--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.90,0:35:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  这个周末  真的是  呃  太棒了\N{\fs12}Well, Alvin, the weekend was, uh... fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.64,0:35:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.07,0:35:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是\N{\fs12}It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.67,0:35:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,太感谢你了  呃  关于我的儿子\N{\fs12}And thank you, uh... with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.18,0:35:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的安排\N{\fs12}Thanks for setting that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.20,0:35:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  谢谢\N{\fs12}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.47,0:35:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,捎你一段吗\N{\fs12}Need a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.74,0:35:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  有人来接我  - 就知道会这样\N{\fs12}- No, I've got it. - I'm sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.77,0:36:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.73,0:36:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,玩的开心吗\N{\fs12}Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.62,0:36:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很开心\N{\fs12}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.31,0:36:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没惹麻烦吧\N{\fs12}Did you stay out of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.46,0:36:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧\N{\fs12}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.13,0:36:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs12}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.90,0:36:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你回来了\N{\fs12}Hey. You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.49,0:36:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我就是来看看你\N{\fs12}Sorry to just drop in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.18,0:36:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.87,0:36:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我  只是  呃  好吧  我很想看看你\N{\fs12}I just, uh-- Well, I really wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.21,0:36:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\fs12}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.33,0:37:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想你离开\N{\fs12}I don't want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  这样很好  但是  呃\N{\fs12}Well, that's kind, Lulu, but, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.32,0:37:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  这是你的事务所\N{\fs12}Alvin, this is your clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.52,0:37:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说  我在这  但是  我只是\N{\fs12}I mean, I'm here, but, I'm just--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.68,0:37:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是你的事务所  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- This is your clinic. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.93,0:37:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你会留下来吗\N{\fs12}So you'll stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.99,0:37:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我留下来吗\N{\fs12}You want me to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.21,0:37:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然  - 为什么  因为我生病了吗\N{\fs12}- Yes. - Why? Because I'm sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.96,0:37:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为  因为你是不可或缺的\N{\fs12}Because... you're indispensable...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不论你信不信\N{\fs12}believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.68,0:37:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.60,0:37:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  我  呃\N{\fs12}You know, l, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.30,0:37:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你的客户度过了愉快的一个周末\N{\fs12}I had an interesting weekend with one of your clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.47,0:37:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是么  - 蒂凡尼·斯科维奇\N{\fs12}- Really? - Tiffany·Skovich?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.65,0:38:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  - 最近怎么样  伯尼\N{\fs12}- Alvin. - How are you, Bernie?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.23,0:38:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的\N{\fs12}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.21,0:38:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么我能帮你的吗\N{\fs12}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.75,0:38:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是  呃  想为我之前说的话道歉\N{\fs12}I just, uh, want to apologize for saying what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.84,0:38:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时说把它推到你的屁股里什么的很过分\N{\fs12}I was way out of line telling you to shove it up your ass like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.00,0:38:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我来这的主要原因是我的客户  蒂凡尼·斯科维奇\N{\fs12}But the main reason I'm here is my client Tiffany·Skovich.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.22,0:38:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要让她重新回到简之家\N{\fs12}I need to get her back into Jane's Place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.27,0:38:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  她因为反复违反宵禁要求被开除了\N{\fs12}Uh, she was expelled for repeated curfew violations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.33,0:38:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  她爱上了一个塞威克利预科学校的男孩\N{\fs12}Well, she fell in love with a boy from Sewickley Prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.37,0:38:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不想他把她送到\N{\fs12}Didn't want him to drop her off
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.65,0:38:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一个未成年妓女的陪护所  你明白吗\N{\fs12}at a shelter for teenage hookers, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.47,0:38:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能理解  但是  - 她值得再给一次机会\N{\fs12}- I understand but, uh-- - She deserves another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.60,0:38:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 已经给了她四次机会了  - 那就再给她第五次吧\N{\fs12}- She's already had four. - Then give her five.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.92,0:38:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  很抱歉\N{\fs12}No. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.17,0:38:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经是很多年的朋友了  伯尼\N{\fs12}We've been friends a long time, Bernie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.95,0:38:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.70,0:38:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能理解\N{\fs12}Want you to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.61,0:38:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我得了肌萎缩侧索硬化症\N{\fs12}I have ALS.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.05,0:38:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪  阿尔文  真的是太遗憾了\N{\fs12}My, God, Alvin. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.95,0:38:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  也会不要求你帮更多的忙了\N{\fs12}So... won't be asking you for many more favors,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.02,0:38:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,反正也不会太久了\N{\fs12}not for much longer anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.51,0:38:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在情感勒索我\N{\fs12}You're manipulating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.58,0:38:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.74,0:39:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fs12}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.65,0:39:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你要找我吗\N{\fs12}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.73,0:39:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  嘿  快请进\N{\fs12}Yeah, hey. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.72,0:39:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fs12}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.10,0:39:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最近怎么样\N{\fs12}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.57,0:39:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.67,0:39:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  呃\N{\fs12}Listen, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.13,0:39:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的关于尼古拉斯的事情\N{\fs12}what you said about Nicholas...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.95,0:39:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你说的有道理\N{\fs12}I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.68,0:39:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很多时候  我更偏爱他\N{\fs12}There are times when I favor him...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.97,0:39:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我就是希望你能明白  呃\N{\fs12}and I just wanted you to know that, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.48,0:39:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会时刻记住的\N{\fs12}I'm going to keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.99,0:39:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.01,0:39:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,发型不错\N{\fs12}Your hair looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.69,0:39:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  尼克  - 嘿  杰克\N{\fs12}- Hi, Nick. - Hey, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.52,0:40:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那  呃  爸爸  呃  关于周末\N{\fs12}So uh, Dad, uh, about the weekend--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.53,0:40:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你说过是私事的\N{\fs12}Well, I thought you said it was personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.66,0:40:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你说过的\N{\fs12}I'll take you at your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.07,0:40:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.35,0:40:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是能解释为什么我一定要走\N{\fs12}Well, I can explain why I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.75,0:40:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你之前说过的  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}I'll take you at your word, Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.70,0:40:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.23,0:40:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她不肯放过我\N{\fs12}She won't let me off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.43,0:40:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.59,0:40:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉维多利亚了  但她仍然想跟我结婚\N{\fs12}I told Victoria. She still wants to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.02,0:40:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好消息\N{\fs12}Well, that's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.91,0:40:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  不管你想不想  这个伴郎你是做定了\N{\fs12}So, like it or not, you're stuck being my Best Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.90,0:40:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\fs12}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.12,0:40:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想  那个治愈者\N{\fs12}I've been thinking... about that healer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.64,0:40:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.70,0:40:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谁又知道呢\N{\fs12}Well, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.79,0:40:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可能就有效果了  - 很可能\N{\fs12}- Maybe it worked. - Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.96,0:40:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果没有效果  - 但是  可能会有效果\N{\fs12}- If it didn't... - Well, maybe it did work.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.28,0:41:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卢·格里克的最后一季  1939\N{\fs12}Lou Gehrig's final season-- 1939.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.85,0:41:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他遇到些问题  没人知道是什么问题\N{\fs12}Something was wrong with him, didn't know what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.15,0:41:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他仍然打了八场  还有四个安打\N{\fs12}He still played in eight games. Still got four hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.52,0:41:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 四个吗  - 之前一年\N{\fs12}- Four? - Year before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.31,0:41:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他死前三年\N{\fs12}three years before he died...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.01,0:41:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,格里克打了.295\N{\fs12}Gehrig batted .295,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.54,0:41:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,打了29个本垒打\N{\fs12}hit 29 home runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.37,0:41:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 29  - 哇哦\N{\fs12}- 29. -Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.00,0:41:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想想这个  尼克\N{\fs12}Think about it, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.18,0:41:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是厉害\N{\fs12}That's a lot of hitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.02,0:41:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪\N{\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.06,0:41:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次了  你知道的\N{\fs12}This is it. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.82,0:41:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,决不允许再错过宵禁\N{\fs12}No more missing curfews.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.20,0:41:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.38,0:41:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我说真的  我\N{\fs12}I mean it. l--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.86,0:41:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以后再遇到这种情况我也帮不了你了\N{\fs12}I can't keep getting you out of these situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.22,0:41:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  蒂凡尼  你得把我的钥匙还给我了\N{\fs12}And, Tiffany, you're going to have to give me my key back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.71,0:41:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好孩子  蒂凡尼\N{\fs12}You're a great kid, Tiffany.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.40,0:41:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量乖一点\N{\fs12}Try to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.62,0:41:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你们先到我办公室等一下吧  我马上就到\N{\fs12}Uh... you can step into my office. I'll be right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.85,0:41:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了她钥匙吗\N{\fs12}You gave her your key?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.00,0:42:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没有\N{\fs12}I did no such thing.


